# An Experimental Comparison of Complex Object Implementations for Big Data Systems

Java
--
Java Implementation is in Directory ./Java

C++
--
C++ Implementation is in Direcotry ./C++ 

Rust
--
Rust Implementation is in Direcotry ./Rust
